data.description: This 3 bed 2 bath Cherry Creek home is located on a large corner lot on a quiet cul-de-sac. The home features hardwood flooring in kitchen and dining room, granite tile flooring and counters in bathrooms, crown molding and wainscoting in dining room, recessed lighting, large backyard for entertaining, and a Spanish tile roof.  Bordering Clover Springs and with Porterfield Creek Trails Open Space Preserve just around the corner, the location delivers. This won't last long.
